reviewText: I needed the Larry Crowne movie for a project in my public speaking class.
One disk works but the other one doesn't.
Some really good comedies and I really needed to laugh a lot after major surgery. Best medicine is laughter.
Be careful we bought this for a friend and I just found out two of the DVDs were missing from the package
I love Tom Hanks. period. And Julia Roberts. Larry Crowne is an awesome movie. The other movies are great in the collection. Great value!!
I ENJOYED the movie " Because I Said So " it's worth buying just for that one !
